<doc id="1333785" wikidata="Q7129412" url="?curid=1333785" title="Pampas grass">
<text>Pampas grass or pampas-grass or Pap&#x27;s grass is a common name which may refer to any of several similar-looking, tall-growing species of grass: 

* Species of &quot;Cortaderia&quot; including:
:* &quot;Cortaderia selloana&quot; and its selected cultivars
:* &quot;Cortaderia jubata&quot; (Andean pampas grass, purple pampas grass)
* &quot;Erianthus ravennae&quot; (syn. &quot;Saccharum ravennae&quot;) (giant woolly-beard grass, hardy pampas grass, Ravenna grass, ekra)
* &quot;Miscanthus sinensis&quot; (Japanese pampas grass)</text><links>
